reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It's everything I wanted.
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a portable lamp to take on trips with me. Little did I realize how much I would end up loving this desk lamp. It's easy to put together, so if I want to take it apart to pack in my suitcase, reassembly is super easy. It's actually compact enough you don't have to take it apart to pack with you, depending upon your packing space. I really love the gooseneck to redirect light where I want it. The lighting can be programmed for reading, or brighter for work projects, and it has a nightlight. It has a light slide so you can raise or lower the brightness. It's sturdy, lightweight, and it's design will fit most decors without being obtrusive.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Made in USA
reviews.reviewText: I first check manufacturers and went with this produce because they are made here in the beautiful USA!The product was SO easy to assemble and works perfect. There’s a special setting for using it near a computer screen, reduces glare. I have ZERO shadowsg on my desk and I can SEE everything without straining my eyes. Great product and I will definitely be checking with this manufacturer for any future lighting purchases!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Finally found desk lamp that works for me
reviews.reviewText: Took 3 tries but this Lepower desk lamp is it. Good construction and weight of base. Great controls on the base not on a cord. Light output brightness and levels are perfect. Like the blue dot on base at on/off button to see in dark to turn on. Very satisfied. Thank you Amazon for the easy reyturn policy, took 3 buys and 2 returns to settle on this lamp.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Bought this for my husband. He loves it. He loves the different settings and it isn't in the way. Only thing was one piece was missing so he couldn't use it right away. The company replaced it and all is good!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I really like this lamp. It’s streamlined, and illuminates a large area clearly in several modes. What I like best is that there is no annoying glare. I had purchased a lamp previously that was over one hundred dollars. I got a headache whenever I used it, and couldn’t see the colors or details of my craft items very well due to a terrible glare. I am very happy with this purchase and appreciate the very affordable price! I highly recommend it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this light to use on my six-seater dining table to make jig saw puzzles. Its great! Very bright with a large coverage area. It was well packaged and went together easily. It has brightness adjustments and a timer. Doubt I'll ever use those options, but they are there.
